Title: Sister
Description: ['An original song by Eve featuring Vocaloid Hatsune Miku, animated by Avogado6. A re-arranged version of the song was also included on Eve\'s 3rd album "Official Number" released October 16, 2016 on his own self-made record label ', harapeco records, '. Eve also created a self-cover on February 1, 2018.']
